Revision history for perl module Sys::Virt

11.10.0 2025-12-00

 - Add VIR_DOMAIN_BACKUP_BEGIN_PRESERVE_SHUTDOWN_DOMAIN constant
 - Add VIR_DOMAIN_EVENT_SUSPENDED_GUEST_SHUTDOWN constant

