 - Add VIR_DOMAIN_SAVE_PARAM_PARALLEL_CHANNELS constant
 - Add VIR_ERR_AGENT_COMMAND_TIMEOUT and VIR_ERR_AGENT_COMMAND_FAILED constants
 - Add support for NIC MAC change event

